{"tid":1912560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"德州男子超市舔雪糕再放回雪櫃 將被判囚30日","createTime":"2020-03-06T07:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T04:32:17.000Z","uid":185631,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"64cbe2e20a0dbf0e582088374444285ff46d7062","tid":1912560,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:15:41.000Z","msg":"美國德州阿瑟港於8月26日晚在當地一間超市內取出一盒家庭裝雪糕，並打開蓋子用舌頭舔入面的雪糕，再放回雪櫃，被判入獄30天。<br />\n<br />\n24歲的安德森（D&rsquo;Adrien Anderson）的視頻於去年8月在社交媒體上分享在沃爾瑪超市打開一盒雪糕，然後嬉皮笑臉地不斷舔入面的雪糕，更用手指把雪糕挖出來品嘗。他其後把雪糕放回雪糕，露出得意洋洋的表情。根據沃爾瑪超市的閉路電視片段，其實安德森最終有購買該盒雪糕，但他自己上傳的影片中，沒有拍攝買雪糕的過程。<br />\n<br />\n然而，為了安全起見，冰淇淋製造商Blue Bell Creameries還是替換了冰櫃中的所有冰淇淋，費用為1,565美元。<br />\n<br />\n他還被判處六個月緩刑，100小時無償工作，罰款1,000美元（770英鎊），並被勒令向冰淇淋公司支付1,565美元。<br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司美國廣播公司報導說，安德森和他的父親後來回到商店給官員看一張收據，以證明他已經購買了受污染的冰淇淋。<br />\n<br />\n安德森（Anderson）今年早些時候認罪，罪名是輕罪刑事惡作劇。<br />\n<br />\n對另一個德克薩斯冰淇淋冰淇淋店的憤怒<br />\n<br />\n沃爾瑪在被捕時發表的一份聲明中說：&ldquo;如果食品被篡改，或者顧客想留下留下摻假產品的印象，我們將迅速採取執法行動，以識別，逮捕和起訴那些人。誰以為這是個玩笑-事實並非如此。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n安德森的冰淇淋特技是在一個非常相似的視頻之後一個月出現的。在這段視頻中，一個十幾歲的女孩舔了一桶冰淇淋，然後將其放回得克薩斯州拉夫金的沃爾瑪的冰櫃中。<br />\n<br />\n在那種情況下，當時不到18歲的那個女孩後來沒有買冰淇淋。她舔冰淇淋的視頻被觀看了超過1300萬次。"},{"pid":"acd28cd45e669666c31a4d2c2f2609336a47c03c","tid":1912560,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:32:02.000Z","msg":"條女奶過杯雪糕喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7676632d92964848d590c5716d8269460135dee","tid":1912560,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:34:19.000Z","msg":"射埋精仲得了！？"},{"pid":"acd4193094b77777d90e6373499253f30fb545b6","tid":1912560,"uid":66514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"死力架"},{"pid":"5636b44bc1deb14af65c1486f3a4cfb520c5d8d1","tid":1912560,"uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:36:21.000Z","msg":"點解啲雪糕唔揾啲紙/膠面啤實？"},{"pid":"3e311d5561b82102dc27d93923d2baf4b9db0f68","tid":1912560,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:36:34.000Z","msg":"人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acfaaa5d9c1810a1ba38a923daa406d9910ce96","tid":1912560,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e311d5561b82102dc27d93923d2baf4b9db0f68","tid":1912560,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:36:34.000Z","msg":"人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:23:08.000Z","msg":"直情係賤人一名!"},{"pid":"76634e9f712fdbf78242a02770c08ea6181552a9","tid":1912560,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/D845/production/_111156355_anderson.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F320%2Fcpsprodpb%2FD845%2Fproduction%2F_111156355_anderson.jpg&h=49db7fbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c49c62040da682029f3ff92dd8230561458a629f","tid":1912560,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"76634e9f712fdbf78242a02770c08ea6181552a9","tid":1912560,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/D845/production/_111156355_anderson.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F320%2Fcpsprodpb%2FD845%2Fproduction%2F_111156355_anderson.jpg&h=49db7fbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:32:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想比佢碌大黑腸屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌完請佢食雪榚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}